{
  "stem": "4187.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't have shoes-- some sort of clog that we were clogging around.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But you learned to walk in those things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But one's got to remember that Auschwitz at night in July is bitterly cold.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, our [INAUDIBLE] appels started at 4:00 AM, so we were herded out at 4 o'clock in the morning in that petticoat, and stood there for God knows how long-- four hours, whatever, just in that petticoat.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you know, we never got sick.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Isn't that amazing?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We never got sick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Was that every day?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes, every morning.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Every morning and every afternoon for about four or five hours, whatever, because they counted you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, again, I'm jumping ahead.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we had these petticoats, and then from there, we were marched into the actual compound.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How long that march was, I have absolutely no idea.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One thing I cannot remember, and that's the geography.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember the geography of the camp I was in which, was C Lager-- C Lager, Lager C.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But that's the only geography I remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I cannot put together the rest of the camp, because you weren't allowed out of your lager, naturally.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the once or twice when they took you somewhere, you went, and you didn't know where you went.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So anyhow, I'm no good on the geography.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Anyway, we were taken into this this C Lager, and the barrack that we were taken to was, to the best of my remembrance-- and I'd just about stake my life on that-- was number 12.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now, that was a barrack for young women.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were all pretty young.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, what shall I say to you?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were the beds-- did I say beds?-- were on top of each other.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
